Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求。。求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要钱的话多少都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要我的命。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的。。脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第六话\N黑夜来的访问者黑笠现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样各位觉得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了？\N这可是我卷起袖子做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总该表示些意见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊。左之助也真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了\N都流出口水来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.91,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.85,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了为了要生存\N必须要忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心每天都吃这个\N你也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，吃小熏小姐所做的菜\N能增加味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很好的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有意见的话不要来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天只是来吃饭的还敢有意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不找人打架后就没钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得小里小气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然闯进来真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察署长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察署长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N前些日子增加各位的麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天有什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村先生今天我是来\N拜托你一件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到政府的威信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前\N新闻也把这件事封锁起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你\N请你把这个杀人魔打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人称黑笠是非常厉害的剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这十年\N那家伙锁定的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是一些政府的大人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他以前也是维新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前也是维新志士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙先送警告书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后闯进来破坏警察的警备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.96,0:05:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人对他来说\N简直是一件快乐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲者之中\N也有很多的女性及小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样，为什么不用枪打他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.31,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然每回也配备了拳枪警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是还没拔枪之前\N全员都被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪还没拔就被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫黑笠的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕跟小生一样\N是之前幕府的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使明治过了十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心已被血的颜色及味道所夺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法停止杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！时间快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是黑笠所警告的十二点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托各位了，杀了那家伙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会照各位所希望的钱付给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.71,0:07:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那黑笠来了\N我们会把他给杀了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么连你也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么玩意儿\N这么有趣的打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能只让你一个人表现吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是打架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.59,0:07:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是还没拔枪\N全部都被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，恐怕是。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想到什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心里有什么线索吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会知道\N黑笠那家伙的真正身份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是警告的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁。。是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在里面，在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N最前面由小生和左之助来防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人跟在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还。。没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在装腔作势唬人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.93,0:09:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿。。都在都在。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道命运的虫也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一。。二。。三。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十四，十五只比想象中的还要少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个目眼。。太危陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙由我来对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷大人拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快。快上！打倒那家伙后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会付五倍的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:09:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会让他做陆军的仕官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五倍。。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了。。我接受！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也接受了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西\N为了欲望要舍弃生命吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，这种感觉真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃走！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.44,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫黑笠的男人。。\N恐怕跟小生一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是以前幕府末年的杀人者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好的预感。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身。。身体动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃了可不行我拔了一次剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论是哪一位都要被我杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话就没有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以动吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象不是一般的蝼蚁之辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我先砍哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手吗。。头吗。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.69,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二阶堂平法心之一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一种名称居缩之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末年在京都有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用眼睛发出来的气\N来跟敌人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使对手没办法移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是善于使用心之一方的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮浪杀人者鹳堂刃卫！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用飞天剑流的传说中的志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左边脸颊\N有大的十字伤口的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村拔刀斋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.13,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣\N已经好久不曾有过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟拔刀斋见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象回到那怀念的幕府时代。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因金钱跟权力而腐败的猪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把目标改成你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来。最强的维新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心之一方是意志跟意志的胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有跟你相同的剑气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会被制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幕府末年杀了很多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了要看到血而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不分敌人或同伴。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是和平的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日常中杀人的幕府时代\N已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了你自己觉醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是听错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被歌颂成\N非常冷血的杀人者拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心已经不是杀人者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.73,0:13:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末年之后\N已经决定不杀任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈。。。笨蛋家伙！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太没趣了！太没趣了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你跟幕府末年的拔刀斋\N差太远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者不杀人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要十年不杀人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑气就会退步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己应该明白才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体能动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只给你一天的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那时侯给我回到以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧。回到冷血的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想杀的\N是那幕府末年的拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！那混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全的让他走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是你成为目标了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，应该说是个好时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你。。你从一开始就猜测会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才接受拜托的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许正如那家伙所说的\N也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的小生恐怕赢不了那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小生要打败那家伙。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末年\N以杀人而存在的同志。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我来说\N是不可避免的一场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象没我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之我有事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去帮我传话给小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种年纪的姑娘\N不该让我看到这种脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象昨天担心剑心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一晚都没有睡的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了剑心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的话不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不回来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要跟黑笠战斗\N而要舍弃一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃一切。。？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到这里看到你们后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会姑息自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不回来让自己集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说没办法打倒那怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他或许打算\N要回到以前的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂。！你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗\N当然是去找剑心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想对他绑手绑脚的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑笠跟一般的对手可不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。剑心已经打算\N不回到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊一定是打算不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒黑笠后就会回到以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样打算去流浪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是流浪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道什么时候\N再到哪里去流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲跟我母亲死后。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时侯连剑心也要离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.55,0:18:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要剩下我一个人。。不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟剑心分离觉得不安受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是娇生惯养的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.47,0:18:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的心情跟娇生惯养\N是脱不了关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样快找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊那小姐要做些什么，不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点找到她不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能赢那家伙吗。。用逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。。。心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到你了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比刃卫还要可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不回道场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起跟你在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫的事你听说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说了，可是我不回去。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果为了保卫谁而战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法赢刃卫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏小姐。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最中意的蓝色发带。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借给剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生没有要借。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要借
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？总之只是借给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟刃卫战斗完后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了有这回事\N而就这样出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.16,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，一定会拿回来还你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安心在道场等我回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,。。那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样约定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位小姑娘是你的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气吧！生气吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.29,0:21:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到十年前原来的你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恨我吧憎恨我吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到杀人的拔刀斋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫
